name: Sofia Perez
summary: Sofia Perez is a 29-year-old Software Engineer from San Diego, California, currently living in Los Angeles. She is a graduate of the University of California who values ambition, family, and independence. Sofia is a multi-lingual woman who speaks both English and Spanish fluently. She identifies as a straight woman with a Hispanic/Latino ethnicity. Her interests include traveling, cooking, and reading. Even though she is agnostic and politically Liberal, she is looking for a life partner who believes in monogamy. Sofia doesn't have children but is open to starting a family. A Libra at heart, she prefers the company of people who are energetic and active like her. Her love for animals is evident as she owns a cat. Although she enjoys an occasional drink, Sofia remains firm about her non-smoking status and doesn't partake in marijuana use or drugs. She prefers a partner who is between 29 and 35 years old, exercises regularly, and does not smoke or use drugs.
